{"tid":853378,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人類幾時先可以再有突破？","createTime":"2018-10-08T14:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T14:51:44.000Z","uid":139907,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91ab55a636bcc461b4763110c0fb41ae9c10a88e","tid":853378,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:14:30.000Z","msg":"以前既人類真係好撚勁<br />\n有自己意識 可以適應到唔同物理環境<br />\n可能每發現個大陸就做地主 令其他生物絕種<br />\n就算先天條件差（身體上） 都可以製造武器 毛皮保護自己<br />\n擔心無穩定糧食 就開始農業革命<br />\n轉食農作物之後 人類既身體同腸胃都有所進化 同開始長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過安逸開始令佢地唔再進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係想守住作物<br />\n當時既人類每件事都靠自己開發 領悟<br />\n<br />\n但點解今時今日 就只剩低返工同無聊同疏離？<br />\n點解會倒退緊<br />\n<br />\n個個沉迷社交網絡 電子器材 表現自我<br />\n咁樣人類既身體係唔會進化架！<br />\n<br />\n點解人類愈黎愈廢"},{"pid":"a17639e7bca0875cdd93f21c125aa969f394bcc8","tid":853378,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"你錯啦 進化到機械人唔飲唔食照下太陽能又一日"},{"pid":"91d60ac62ac9a0da6a043c0528952f8a892988d8","tid":853378,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17639e7bca0875cdd93f21c125aa969f394bcc8","tid":853378,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"你錯啦 進化到機械人唔飲唔食照下太陽能又一日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"咁植物同動物有咩用"},{"pid":"72c8a6cd8fcffe6d4d201a9f7ba7a0ff6bbde394","tid":853378,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17639e7bca0875cdd93f21c125aa969f394bcc8","tid":853378,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"你錯啦 進化到機械人唔飲唔食照下太陽能又一日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:20:30.000Z","msg":"喂屌，理想生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50496c0b4e985bd30e3366ccc5f227c4ec67d5f","tid":853378,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,